        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Rosetta', 3: 'I was just venting a little battlefield pressure. My M.I.N.D. hasn\\'t been entirely stable lately, and I need to regulate myself—for my sake, and to keep things easier for you, Commandant.', 4: '1'}"
